  rulesTitle: Infinite Knight Run
  rulesText: "Control a lone white knight on an endless board.\n\nMove using
    standard knight jumps (L-shape).\n\nAvoid squares attacked by black pieces
    and holes.\nYou can capture unprotected black pieces.\nProtected pieces and
    their attack zones are off limits.\n\nThe board gets harder as you climb.\nYour
    score is the max distance reached.\n\nGame ends when no legal moves remain."
